<function>

access:   public

name: isoDate

param: mixed, $value

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that a value is an ISO 8601 date string.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.

The format is "yyyy-mm-dd".  Also checks to see that the date
itself is valid (e.g., no Feb 30).